iv><p>Contact me at : <a href="mailTo:contact@matthewsullivan.media">contact@matthewsullivan.media</a></p></div></div></div></noscript><script>(function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i['GoogleAnalyticsObject']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){(i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o),m=s.getElementsByTagName(o)[0];a.async=1;a.src=g;m.parentNode.insertBefore(a,m)})(window,document,'script','https://www.google-analytics.com/analytics.js','ga');ga('create','UA-83714838-1','auto');ga('send','pageview');</script><div class=body-border><nav class=navbar><div class="container text-center"><img src="assets/images/logo/logo-dark.png" alt=logo class=logo width=200 height=200 /><a data-toggle=collapse data-target="#side-menu" class="toggle-menu menu-right pull-right push-body nav-icon"><span class=sr-only>Toggle Navigation</span><span class=icon-bar></span><span class=icon-bar></span><span class=icon-bar></span></a><div class="collapse navbar-collapse center-block"><ul class="navbar-nav navigation-symbol"><li> <a href="#about">ABOUT</a></li><li><a href="#services">SERVICES</a></li><li> <a href="#works">FOLIO</a></li><li> <a href="#contact">CONTACT</a></li></ul></div><div id=side-menu class="cbp-spmenu cbp-spmenu-vertical cbp-spmenu-right text-left"><img src="assets/images/logo/logo-light-nobackground.png" width=75 height=56 alt=Logo /><a href="#" class=close-menu><i class="icon ion-ios-close-empty icon-close menu-close-btn"></i></a><ul class=nav><li> <a href="#about">ABOUT</a></li><li> <a href="#services">SERVICES</a></li><li> <a href="#works">FOLIO</a></li><li> <a href="#contact">CONTACT</a></li></ul><p class=copyright>COPYRIGHT © 2020 Matthew Sullivan Media</p></div></div></nav><nav id=scroll-nav class="navbar-fixed hidden"><div class="container text-center"><div class=navbar-brand><img src="assets/images/logo/logo-light-nobackground.png" width=75 height=56 alt=Logo /></div><a data-toggle=collapse data-target="#side-menu" class="toggle-menu menu-right pull-right push-body nav-icon-fixed-menu collapsed"><span class=sr-only>Toggle Navigation</span><span class=icon-bar></span><span class=icon-bar></span><span class=icon-bar></span></a><div class="collapse navbar-collapse"><ul class="navbar-nav-fixed pull-right"><li> <a href="#about">ABOUT</a></li><li> <a href="#services">SERVICES</a></li><li> <a href="#works">FOLIO</a></li><li> <a href="#contact">CONTACT</a></li></ul></div></div></nav><div class=go-top><i class=ion-android-arrow-dropup-circle></i></div><div class=full-height-border><div id=head_panel_slider class=owl-carousel><div class="item full-height-border vertical-middle text-center section-overlay-dark background-slide-1 container"><div class="inner animated fadeIn minimal-white with-cross row"><div class=col-md-12><div class=row><div class=col-md-12><i></i><h2>Software Engineer</h2><div class=row><div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4"><p>More than just a Developer. I am a well rounded Media Specialist who has a keen interest in leadership.</p><a href="#works" class="btn btn-success animated fadeInUp">PORTFOLIO</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="item full-height-border vertical-middle text-center section-overlay-dark background-slide-2 container"><div class="inner animated fadeIn minimal-white with-cross row"><div class=col-md-12><div class=row><div class=col-md-12><i></i><h2>Passionate Teacher</h2><div class=row><div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4"><p>Not only building, and consulting, but teaching others the lingo of the web and media.</p><a href="#cv" class="btn btn-success animated fadeInUp">Curriculum Vitae</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><section id=about class="section section-dark text-center"><div class=container><header class=section-head><span>01</span><h2>ABOUT</h2><p>Enthuiastic and Experienced Software Developer</p></header><div class="about-content with-divider-thickline-small row"><div class="col-md-offset-2 col-xs-12 col-md-8 padded"><div class=row><div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 padding-top margin-top"><h3 data-os-animation=fadeInUp data-os-animation-delay=0s class=os-animation>Hello</h3><span data-os-animation=fadeInUp data-os-animation-delay=0s class=os-animation></span><p data-os-animation=fadeInUp data-os-animation-delay=0s class=os-animation>My name is Matthew Sullivan. I am a Software Engineer, Team Lead, & Multimedia Specialist who is fascinated in all aspects of media production.</p> <p data-os-animation=fadeInUp data-os-animation-delay=.2s class=os-animation> Driven by a passion to produce highly efficient, maintainable codebases while keeping unparalleled attention to detail. I have a proven track record of solid development and leadership strategies. Moving forward, I hope to continue to build relationships and foster healthy team environments.</p><a href="#cv" data-os-animation=fadeInUp data-os-animation-delay=.4s class="btn-link pull-left os-animation">Check out my CV</a></div><div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12"><img src="assets/images/about/about-image-1.jpg" alt="About Image" class=small-screen-margin-top width=400 height=600 /></div></div></div><div class=col-md-4><img src="assets/images/about/about-image-2.jpg" alt="About Image" width=400 height=850 /></div><div class="col-md-4 margin-top padding-top"><h3 data-os-animation=fadeInUp data-os-animation-delay=0s class=os-animation>Interests</h3><span data-os-animation=fadeInUp data-os-animation-delay=0s class=os-animation> </span><p data-os-animation=fadeInUp data-os-animation-delay=0s class=os-animation>Time management plays a huge roll in my day to day life. Late is not an option for me. I have the ability to handle a lot of work at once, and I enjoy learning new things while problem solving. Outside of work I enjoy:</p><ul data-os-animation=fadeInUp data-os-animation-delay=0s class="featured-list text-left os-animation"><li>Playing music</li><li>Listening to music</li><li>Listening to podcasts</li><li>Reading</li><li>Gardening</li><li>Jogging and hiking</li><li>Healthy lifestyles</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section id=video-intro class="section section-nopadding-bottom section-black text-center"><header class="section-head padded-big"><h2>Demo Reel</h2><p>Have a look at my demo reel.</p></header><div class="video-intro section section-short section-dark"><i data-os-animation=video-line data-os-animation-delay=0s class=os-animation></i><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nQa72e_cC5I" class=popup-youtube><img src="assets/images/misc/video-image.jpg" width=900 height=499 alt="Video Image"/><span></span></a></div></section><section id=services class="section section-dark text-center padding-bottom-fix"><div class=container><header class=section-head><span>02</span><h2>SERVICES</h2><p>Full Stack in more ways than one.</p></header><div class=row><div data-os-animation=fadeInUp data-os-animation-delay=0s class="col-md-3 os-animation"><div class="icon-block icon-block-dark"><i class=ion-iphone></i><h3>iOS Development</h3><p>Starting in Objective-C in 2014, I now have a core understanding of iOS development and the Xcode environment. I am very familiar with Objective-C and Swift.</p></div></div><div data-os-animation=fadeInUp data-os-animation-delay=.1s class="col-md-3 small-screen-margin-top os-animation"><div class="icon-block icon-block-dark"><i class=ion-ios-monitor-outline></i><h3>Web Development</h3><p>A true web developer who knows how to get things done without Wordpress. Both front-end and back-end. From JavaScript to PHP - I am capable of small to large scale projects.</p></div></div><div data-os-animation=fadeInUp data-os-animation-delay=.2s class="col-md-3 small-screen-margin-top os-animation"><div class="icon-block icon-block-dark"><i class=ion-edit></i><h3>Design</h3><p>The Adobe Suite? No problem. I have the knowledge to create a beautiful logo, all the way to a complete application design. </p></div></div><div data-os-animation=fadeInUp data-os-animation-delay=.3s class="col-md-3 small-screen-margin-top os-animation"><div class="icon-block icon-block-dark"><i class=ion-chatbubbles></i><h3>Consultation</h3><p>I am available to aid in the process of UI/UX design as well as help design the architecture of new or old platforms. High standards in code maintainability and cleanliness are a must.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section section-black background-team-quote"><div class=container><div class="absolute-top-content text-center"><div class=team-member-quote-intro><span>368 Durham</span><h3>WORD ON THE STREET</h3><i data-os-animation=team-quote-line data-os-animation-delay=0s class=os-animation></i></div></div><div class=row><div class=col-md-12><div class="text-center team-member-quote"><img src="assets/images/misc/brian.jpg" width=80 height=80 alt="368 Durham Quote" class=img-circle /><p data-os-animation=fadeInUp data-os-animation-delay=0s class=os-animation>368 Durham has used Matthew as a consult for web design & development for several years on various projects. Matthew brings experience and a fresh outlook to all client projects and has proven to be a great asset in all various aspects.</p><i></i><span data-os-animation=fadeInUp data-os-animation-delay=.6s class=os-animation>Brian Rutherford<small data-os-animation=fadeInUp data-os-animation-delay=.6s class=os-animation>368 Durham</small></span></div></div></div></div></section><section id=works class="section section-dark section-nopadding-bottom text-center"><div class=container-fluid><header class=section-head><span>03</span><h2>WORKS</h2><p>Hand picked projects and case studies.</p></header><div id=content><article><div class=row><div class=col-md-12><i class="filter-icon ion-android-more-vertical rotated"></i><ul class="data-filter-categories margin-bottom padding-bottom"><li><a data-filter="" class=portfolio-filter>ALL </a></li><li><a data-filter=.filter-web class=portfolio-filter>WEB</a></li><li><a data-filter=.filter-apps class=portfolio-filter>APPS </a></li></ul></div>